reviewText: I wish I hadn't waited so long to buy it. It's so rad seeing so much of my childhood Thrasher memories on video.

Yes that's right! this is a blast from skateboarding's past covering the years 93'-02' it pretty much has anyone of importance that was on the scene or still is,although,there is just not enough Penny for me, but that's per usual. Anyway it's got plenty of killer footage of others such as GONZ,CARDS,CAIRO,MJ,KOSTON,SHAO,SENN,MUSKA,ROWLEY,DREHOBL,SANCHEZ and a ton more! Also this set should wet the appetite of you kiddies of today as it has plenty of bangers and skaters of the recent past to present..PJ..anyone?So run dont' walk out and get yours today!
